{"id": "art-54", "label": "Art. 54", "title": "Art. 54", "slug": "art-54", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 54 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_531472534\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2442\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_531472534\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Dup&#259; efectuarea <span class=SpellE>formalit&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nde publicitate în leg&#259;tur&#259; cu persoanele care, ca organe ale <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, sunt autorizate s&#259; o reprezinte,\nsocietatea nu poate opune <span class=SpellE>ter&#355;ilor</span> nicio\nneregularitate la numirea acestora, cu <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span>\ncazului în care societatea face dovada c&#259; <span class=SpellE>ter&#355;ii</span>\nrespectivi aveau <span class=SpellE>cuno&#351;tin&#355;&#259;</span> de\naceast&#259; neregularitate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1990188172\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2441\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1990188172\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Societatea nu poate invoca <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>ter&#355;i</span> numirile în <span class=SpellE>func&#355;iile</span>\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (1) sau încetarea acestor <span class=SpellE>func&#355;ii</span>,\ndac&#259; ele nu au fost publicate în conformitate cu <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>legea</i>.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}